#: ../../discuss/mail_twitter.rst:33
msgid "Getting the API key and secret"
msgstr "正在获取API密钥和机密"

#: ../../discuss/mail_twitter.rst:35
msgid ""
"When on the App dashboard, switch to the **Keys and Access Tokens** tab."
